{
  "stem": "17625.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 179.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Mietek Morawa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He's supposed to be kapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And on-- on-- on a, [SIGHS] you know, since then-- and the SS man comes in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He makes a little bit of a speech, now, that this-- this is work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you work, you'll live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And right away, after that, this Mietek took a-- a-- a-- a-- a-- a hard club.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He start clobbering.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He took us outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Outside, this was the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He took us outside in-- in-- in the-- in the-- in the-- the-- what-- what do you call it in-- in the backyard-- in the front yard, where by the-- by the gate was there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In dark, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I saw a pile-- a piled up frozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't know even what it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he came out with a club.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He says, pull them in!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Pull them in!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't even start.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It-- this was Muselmanns-- dead ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they were frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because there was water on top of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The first was-- was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to-- you had-- we had to part them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to-- we-- we-- we-- we exhausted doing this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he was running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was running after us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we brought them in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then the-- the-- the job was-- there was ovens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was a-- a truck which goes on the wheels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You put up a few bodies, and you push 'em in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They learn you how to do it-- and go into that oven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the one that was holding the bodies-- and they pulled out the oven.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anyway, we stood there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two weeks, maybe three weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
